# ECB Architecture

Use the Entity-Control-Boundary pattern.

## Layers

- `boundary`: 외부 입출력을 담당한다. 예: CLI, UI adapter, API adapter.
- `control`: use case 흐름과 비즈니스 로직 조합을 담당한다.
- `entity`: 도메인 데이터, 값 객체, 도메인 규칙을 담당한다.

## Dependency Direction

- `boundary` may include or depend on `control`.
- `control` may include or depend on `entity`.
- `entity` must not include or depend on `boundary` or `control`.
- Allowed direction is only `boundary -> control -> entity`.
- Keep `entity` free of console I/O, filesystem I/O, networking, and framework code.
